# UX / UI design

## Theme

- Dark product pages: `StarBackground` + `card-twilight` + app-specific accent (sky, emerald, amber, cyan…)
- Legal pages: light gradient + tinted card; accent border matches app
- Utilities in `app/globals.css`: `text-electric-blue`, `twilight-*`, `focus-visible-ring`

## Layout

- Shell: `max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4`
- Legal: `max-w-4xl`; under-construction hero: `max-w-2xl text-center`
- Reuse: `AppIconFrame`, `StoreDownloadBadges`, `DownloadStoreFab`, `LegalSections`

## UX checklist

- One clear primary action per viewport
- User strings in `messages/en.json`, not hardcoded
- RTL: `locale === 'he' || locale === 'ar'` → `text-right`
- Decorative icons: `aria-hidden`; meaningful controls: labels
- Mobile touch targets ≥ 44px; test `md:` icon/heading scale

